summary: Enchanted Ancient Armor Crafting Tools is a crafting set i made for my self to cheat the crap out the crafting and alchemy system without using console commands :D.
descriptionHtml:
Enchanted Ancient Armor Crafting Tools is a crafting set i made for my self to cheat the crap out the crafting and alchemy system without using console commands :D.
I used the ancient draugr set to fool myself into roleplaying and justifying this very overpowered crafting set.
It is actually useful if you're using it for anything other than you're normal gaming or if you don't mind a little cheating and making you're self more powerful armors and weapons.

For whatever reasons anyone can think of i hope you enjoy it. XD
author: JoseNightBreed
